==Useful info==
'''Deep elf zephyrmancers''' are midgame casters that focus on [[Air Magic]]. They are sometimes found in the mid to late [[Dungeon]], and are plentiful in the [[Elven Halls]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*These casters can be dangerous for characters without [[electricity resistance]].
*Pay attention to your surroundings while fighting zephyrmancers, as they can [[doublezap]] you with lightning bolts.

==History==
*Deep elf zephyrmancers were added in [[0.27]] as a single book, electric-focused version of the [[deep elf mage]].

